# ============ STVG code-only .gitignore ============
# --- Data / archive / outputs ---
Inputs/
Outputs/
Archive/
**/eval_runs/
Technical/Assets/
Technical/Data/

# --- C++ / CMake build artifacts (build/ is ~1.8G) ---
**/build/
**/_deps/
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/cmake-build-*/
**/out/
*.o
*.obj
*.a
*.lib
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.exp
nul

# --- JS / frontend ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.svelte-kit/
**/static/assets/

# --- Data / large binary file types ---
*.parquet
*.feather
*.rdb
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.zip
*.7z
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.gz
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.csv
*.tsv
*.pdf
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.psd
*.wav
*.mp3
*.mp4
*.mov
*.h5

# --- Caches ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# --- Virtual envs ---
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# --- Secrets / credentials ---
*.env
.env
.env.*
api_keys*
*.key
*.pem
credentials*
secrets*
*token*
*.secret

# --- IDE / OS ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*.backup_*
.backup_*

# --- Internal session/process docs (Arcanum Publication Hygiene Standard) ---
**/Handoffs/
**/HANDOFF_*.md
**/*HANDOFF*.md
**/PROGRESS_LOG.md
**/*PROGRESS_LOG.md
.claude/
.cursor/
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
**/*_PLAN.md
**/Plans/
**/REBUILD_PLAN.md
**/NEXT_STEPS*.md
**/DECISION_LOG*.md
**/*WISHLIST*.md
**/VISUAL_INSPECTION_*.md
**/PROJECT_HISTORY.md
**/FILE_CATALOG.md
